  "title": "Xtra Umami Norwegian Peppers Fried Rice",
  "description": "A midnight-craving Norwegian dish featuring sweet peppadew peppers and a flexitarian-friendly approach, served on a hot stone plate. This recipe combines umami flavors with a glassy-jelly texture.",
