  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet or wok over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the sliced mushrooms and cook until they are tender and lightly browned.",
    "Add the sliced peppadew peppers and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Add the cooked rice to the skillet or wok, breaking up any clumps with a spatula.",
    "Stir in the soy sauce, sesame oil, salt, and black pepper, and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the crumbled norwegian cheese and stir until it is well combined with the rice mixture.",
    "Transfer the rice mixture to a hot stone plate.",
    "Garnish with chopped scallions and serve immediately."
  ],
